game.description:
It seems that the luck of Ladybug is not into her favor! The foot of this brave lady got injured when she was on her mission and now she is surrounded by an intense pain. Finally, she needs a doctor who could cure his foot problems. Are you searching on a platform where you can practice your doctoring skills? Join Ladybug Foot Surgery game and get ready to try your hands in the latest doctor game for girls where you can put your doctoring abilities to test!
You will get a chance to play the role of a foot doctor in this free online html5 surgery game. Cure her problem with the tools that you see at the bottom of the screen! There are plenty of things to do. Spray water to clean the dirty areas, use the soap to remove all the patches, syringe to clean the red colored patches, remove the thorns and complete other needful steps to make her foot glow again!
Being a foot specialist, you know everything that is required to follow to cure a foot with different kinds of injuries. It will take only a few steps to complete to help the character get a clean and healthy foot. Make sure that you look at the screen to learn what you need to do the next to complete your mobile game. Check out more html5 surgical games for girls that are available to play online for free on multiple devices, including computers, mobile phones and iPhones and iPads!
